<h2>No Solitary Geniuses</h2>
<p>No one designs in a vaccuum. Working in teams allows use to utilize the unique background, training, and natural talents of a variety of people. In the same way that design teams go out and talk to participants during the Discovery phase, they also work as integrated teams
  instead of silo-ing themselves. This allows design teams to hear multiple points during the making phase, in the same way they heard multiple points of view during the Discovery phase.</p>

